snippet.title: Amaranthine Voyage: The Tree of Life Trailer (Hidden object game)
snippet.description:
The official trailer for the upcoming hidden object game by Eipix Entertainment -- Amaranthine Voyage: The Tree of Life Collector's Edition has arrived.

The game will be available soon on www.bigfishgames.com. We hope you enjoy it as much as we do.
